{"tid":1683571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【投票】出來嘅最重要前題係咩？不被捕 定係 要畫面人多？","createTime":"2019-10-30T16:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:43.000Z","uid":74155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dadf7aa43d58998985abdfde4fbd045414ae0160","tid":1683571,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"究竟喺維園or港島無不反，<br />\n明知照入港島會增加勇武被捕風險嘅情況下，<br />\n想問大家覺得邊一樣嘢重要啲？<br />\n係要盡量易出易入減少被圍捕搜捕風險<br />\n抑或係堅持要越多人數越好，<br />\n為嘅就係畫面上多人頭好睇？<br />\n我希望真係要諗清楚邊樣先<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真正首要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不被捕重要啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畫面人頭多重要啲<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得前者重要，請支持<span style=\"color: red;\">港島集會/遊行+五區開花</span><br />\n如果你覺得後者重要啲，即係照原計劃<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界入港島</span>"},{"pid":"915535efa44e609e0f0f0b66a882755c6063739e","tid":1683571,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a9ef0c19b2c2fdc0e34ef973732ef0de818249a","tid":1683571,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}